g gasx that depends on which gasx product you prefer to use click on this link to choose the product you’re interested in then view that product’s drug fact pdf for usage instructions why do i feel bloated when i have gas think of your stomach and intestines like a balloon when they get filled up with more and more gas they expand which makes you feel bloated can i take gasx yes simethicone the active ingredient in gasx works fast without being absorbed into the bloodstream still please use gasx products only as directed can gasx be used if pregnant or nursing when pregnant or nursing ask your doctor before taking any medication can antacids help relieve gas no while some symptoms of gas can mimic heartburn  like discomfort after eating  antacids don’t relieve gas they have a different active ingredient example calcium carbonate that neutralizes the stomach acids coming into contact with your esophagus rather than the buildup of gas in your digestive tract view all products   off save money today get coupon have more questions check out our frequently asked questions visit faqs a better you from the inside out digestive health is a crucial part of overall good health visit our sister brands for more ways to improve your digestive health the easy and convenient way to promote and maintain methylcellulose fiber therapy for irregularity allday allnight heartburn relief with one pill the fiber supplement that’s clear and tastefree trusted treatment for constipation for  years the only fdaapproved overthecounter weightloss aid fastacting extrastrength heartburn relief for fastacting longlasting heartburn relief a better you from the inside out expand for more information a better you from the inside out digestive health is a crucial part of overall good health visit our sister brands for more ways to improve your digestive health the easy and convenient way to promote and maintain methylcellulose fiber therapy for irregularity allday allnight heartburn relief with one pi